    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Gouges having a shank that is either curved for its entire length or straight for most of its length with a sharp bend near the tip.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
